{"tid":646702,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"工程師男仔","createTime":"2018-04-29T09:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T09:39:36.000Z","uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6be3e7880e6b8542d4e62caf7bb76574ec692336","tid":646702,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T09:35:35.000Z","msg":"大家好<br />\n小妹三字頭，普通文員。有個大4年既男同事追我。佢係一個工程師，外國讀書返黎。<br />\n佢外表、打扮十分求其，皮鞋甩皮，唔梳頭，滿臉暗倉。樣子睇洛似4字頭。但佢人係不錯，相處都ok，斯文既。<br />\n我認我港女，但個個都想拖一個企企理理既男朋友出街。但我唔敢同佢講。<br />\n各位師姐、師兄們，你地覺得我要接受佢嗎？"},{"pid":"234c027f643d28c55d46d192856d78e2cb3aa4ed","tid":646702,"uid":33352,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"有牌未？<br />\n無就叫佢走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521898b76643a77526b11f641a843267510b69d7","tid":646702,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T09:37:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6e11790dd99bec8d177c1cbe1cffbe6fc3ce480","tid":646702,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ladies.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27409103&amp;page=1&amp;pid=479356719#pid479356719\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fladies.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D27409103%26page%3D1%26pid%3D479356719%23pid479356719&d=B4vca9ZrPmCa3H5fW8DSS0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=ed2b744f\" target=\"_blank\">http://ladies.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=27409103&amp;page=1&amp;pid=479356719#pid479356719</a><br />\n此po已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}